( ) = te doen
(?) = zou moeten werken nu
(.) = gedeeltelijk gedaan
(x) = gedaan
(-) = doen we nie

Changes (.227 > ?)
------------------------------------
 - Splashscreen
 - userlist
 - system tray
 - ident server
 - links (http, exits, html-entities, colors)
 - implemented some mcp-packages: Statusbar, Client
 - new cool icons
 - auto-linelength updates
 - proxyserver
 - resizeable inputbar
 - autostart sessions
 - Multiline paste in inputbar 
 - Preview pane when browsing for pictures
 - Toolbar-submenu (right-click in the moo to see it)
 - multiline-copy (wrapped lines are now copied as one line, as it should be)
 - fixed bug in logfile that could cause Moops to hang
 - fixed 1024 char limit
 - fixed a few other bugs


